import "./App.scss"
import { Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"
import Home from "./pages/Main"

function App() {
    return (
        <>
			<Routes>
				<Route path="/" exact element={<Main />} />
				<Route path="/my-list" exact element={<MyList />} />
				<Route path="/browse/:id" exact element={<FilmDetails />} />
			</Routes>
        </>
    )
}

export default App
